cters are an exception to this rule. The Free Council will teach any member of their Order rotes of any level, regardless of their Status. It's rumored that the Free Council will even share knowledge with their allies.%0a> %0a> **Furthermore, a mage can only learn a number of rotes equal to the lower of her Intelligence or Resolve at one time. This represents the character’s focus and commitment to being able to retain and understand these esoteric secrets.%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
